title: Alan_Robert's_Killogy_(2013)_(Digital)_(DR_&_Quinch-Empire).
description:
Alan_Robert's_Killogy_(2013)_(Digital)_(DR_&_Quinch-Empire)


Fangoria hails Killogy as an 'INSTANT CLASSIC!' and Bloody Disgusting raves that it's 'One of the most original and unique comics you'll ever lay your eyes on!' Killogy stars Frank Vincent, Marky Ramone and Brea Grant as three murderers trying to piece together their intertwining pasts during a zombie apocalypse. Written and illustrated by the creator of Crawl to Me!
